Get ready for a flavour explosion in your mouth with our mouth-watering grilled tandoori chicken skewers! Served with a refreshing cucumber salad and zesty coriander chutney, these skewers are sure to tantalise your taste buds and leave you wanting more. Perfect for a summer braai or a quick weeknight dinner, these skewers are a must-try! Recipe compliments of Walkersons Hotel & Spa, an elegant five-star establishment hidden in the softly rolling hills of Mpumalanga, close to the popular town of Dullstroom. Serves four. Requires bamboo skewers Side recipes: Yield: four. Prep time: 10min Yield: four portions and a bit more. Prep time: 30min Yield: four. Prep time: 10 mins 